<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我和卢克从一年级开始就是最好的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们干什么都在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们打篮球，骑自行车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们夏天一起游泳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时，我甚至睡在卢克家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是去年，一件很可怕的事发生在卢克身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，他正骑车去公园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他骑得很快，因为他有场棒球比赛，快要迟到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当卢克骑上大路时，他停不下来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克径直驶入路中央。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有辆车开了过来，司机也刹不住车了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车撞上了卢克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>救护车开来把卢克送到了医院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克伤得很重，必须在医院住三个月。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个月后，我终于可以去医院看望他了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很兴奋，问妈妈能不能给卢克带个礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想他会喜欢一个新的足球,</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是妈妈告诉了我一个坏消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卢克现在不能踢球了。因为他的意外，卢克不能走路了。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是什么意思？”我哭道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果卢克不能走路，那他怎么和我玩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还能和谁打篮球？”我对妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是我开始哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还是可以和卢克玩儿。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能和他玩儿了。”我答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是他不能走了，我怎么和他玩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多天，我都没有去医院看卢克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我变得很孤独和悲伤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我试着打篮球，但是不再好玩儿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我去游泳，但是很无聊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是我想起了卢克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我意识到卢克肯定比我更悲伤，更无聊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，在一个周六早晨，我去医院看望了卢克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我到了医院，慢慢地走向他的房门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，我很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我从来没有和一个在事故中受伤的人说过话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我应该跟他说什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许他不想和我做朋友，也许他会很刻薄，很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当我敲门时，我听到了一个熟悉的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是理查德。”我回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我打开门，他就在那儿，坐在轮椅上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不知道对他说什么，我想逃走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看啊！”他喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能用两个轮子移动轮椅。你想看吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”我平静地答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快我和卢克在医院大厅里跑来跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>护士被逼疯了，她让我们停下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是我们玩儿起了卢克的新电子游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天，我们很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我发现卢克还是我曾经的那个朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我觉得有点儿不好意思，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我没有早点来看望他，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我很高兴那天我去了医院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当卢克出院以后，他想做那些我们曾经做过的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想打篮球，他想打棒球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一开始，这些事他都不能做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以卢克有时很生气，有时很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是慢慢地，卢克学会了不用腿去玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他学习用特殊的体育轮椅打篮球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他学会了不用腿去游泳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，在他家人和朋友的帮助下，卢克可以做到他想做的一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当然，卢克因为意外有所改变，但是他还是个很棒的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毫无疑问他还是我的好朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>